{"tid":1594584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[美國國會]美國旗同唱美國歌係價值觀相同","createTime":"2019-09-25T15:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:37:18.000Z","uid":45975,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc7daa15b8b152d0ee5446245ac9f540e89992f","tid":1594584,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R7MIDzBz4WA?start=1967&amp;end=2031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR7MIDzBz4WA%3Fstart%3D1967%26end%3D2031&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=f60a16a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R7MIDzBz4WA?start=1967&amp;end=2031</a><br />\n<br />\n香港示威者在示威中搖著美國的旗幟，唱著美國的國歌，在示威者心中依一個就係自由及民主的象徵，我重覆一次，我們會強大支持香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n依一個係威權社會及民主社會之戰。"},{"pid":"d65602a8fb65837f7bfa35ca74e991a35b3d7f42","tid":1594584,"uid":26013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"點解冇人幫手推下SHARE下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IBXbmlt2k1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIBXbmlt2k1U&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=95e4d240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IBXbmlt2k1U</a>"},{"pid":"6cdfe2de5c6899604784b1f1778a485d51d25426","tid":1594584,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:02:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70c41822bf1172b987b2024456edc3f8455b9dbd","tid":1594584,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6N81OY8_qwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6N81OY8_qwA&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=b6e35208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6N81OY8_qw